# The MASM code of the Token Policy Manager Account Component.
#
# Owns the seven policy-manager storage slots (shared authority, active/allowed maps for
# mint, burn, and transfer) plus the asset-callback storage slots and exposes the management
# procedures for all three policy axes. Pair with at least one mint, burn, and transfer
# policy component whose procedure roots are registered in the allowed-policies maps.

